long_description: company is founded and located at bulandshahr (up) northern part of india. it was founded by two young couples mr.saurabh singh & mrs.chhaya singh by interest to expand business globally. after that we expanded our business on a large scale to provide better quality products by helping work to daily basis workers work on handicrafts & handmade products. company is working in the areas of merchant import and export in india. though there is no limitation for what we trade, our main aim is to bring all indian specialities to the international market. we are bringing all of them to our international customers. we are committed to our customers and suppliers for best and timely services and for transparency in transactions. the mission of "kie xports" is to contribute more and more in enhancement of international trade. our vision is to see global economical growth and elevated quality of living through international business and commerce.
